{"tid":1381972,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【集思廣益】籌旗開一間公司請曬所有被迫害既抗爭者","createTime":"2019-07-29T11:05:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T14:18:37.000Z","uid":37528,"like":40,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"932962324d9e830b00c40795432116433d326677","tid":1381972,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:05:19.000Z","msg":"香港往往就係俾要供樓養家呢個伽鎖搞到個個都唔夠膽出聲，敢怒不敢言<br />\n我地上次一日唔夠已經籌到幾百萬，所以如果有心搞，真係有得搞<br />\n最緊要係可以幫到所有被迫害既抗爭者<br />\n你地並不孤單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db1c1b993d7f995b5faef2bd16fb859cecf5da97","tid":1381972,"uid":37528,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:08:25.000Z","msg":"求教，開士多超市會唔會最易入手？<br />\n唔係為賺錢，係想有個sustainable 既環境去抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1205a7576b01dd5b71fbf46d1ba843e19af0e41","tid":1381972,"uid":271239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"932962324d9e830b00c40795432116433d326677","tid":1381972,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:05:19.000Z","msg":"香港往往就係俾要供樓養家呢個伽鎖搞到個個都唔夠膽出聲，敢怒不敢言<br />\n我地上次一日唔夠已經籌到幾百萬，所以如果有心搞，真係有得搞<br />\n最緊要係可以幫到所有被迫害既抗爭者<br />\n你地並不孤單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:09:07.000Z","msg":"【中學生的聲音】<br />\n<br />\n我哋雖然年紀小，但都希望盡全力發出最大嘅聲音。<br />\n<br />\n學生係未來社會嘅棟樑，所以我哋都有必要為自己，為大家發聲。<br />\n<br />\n雖然呢次係香港最分化嘅一次,但亦都係香港人最團結嘅一次。而我哋中學生都想令大家更團結，所以搞咗今次嘅聯署。<br />\n<br />\n【中學生聯署計劃】<br />\n<br />\n民主運動從來都係先由中學生、大學生發起，因為我哋有一股傻勁，我哋雖然會有衝動嘅時候，但全因為我哋對未來總係抱有無限嘅理想，更願意為理想而付出。<br />\n<br />\n我哋嘅堅持已經令而家好多喺政府部門嘅大人都出咗聲啦，今次就到我哋中學生一齊集氣，比呢個不公義嘅政府聽聽，屬於香港人真正嘅聲音！<br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以係表中填上你嘅學校名，同遮蓋重要個人資料嘅學生證，一齊加入聯署！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdz5V_o8_YiWRVqSsNi9tP1abAHkU0cd7TYr69r1wO1_GyFSA/viewform?usp=pp_url\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSdz5V_o8_YiWRVqSsNi9tP1abAHkU0cd7TYr69r1wO1_GyFSA%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dpp_url&d=SfvWO4iieP9%2B5ivoSMB2Bstxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=56ca2aea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdz5V_o8_YiWRVqSsNi9tP1abAHkU0cd7TYr69r1wO1_GyFSA/viewform?usp=pp_url</a><br />\n<br />\n【A Petition from Secondary School Students for the Solidarity of All Hongkongers]<br />\n<br />\nThe voice of us:<br />\n<br />\nAlthough we are only secondary school students, we try our best to speak up. <br />\n<br />\nStudents are the future pillars of the society, and it is necessary for us to fight for the future and our next generation. <br />\n<br />\nHong Kong is now the most divided, yet Hongkongers are at the same time the most united that we have never seen before.<br />\n<br />\nWe hope we can use our power to make Hongkongers more united, so we initiate this petition.<br />\n<br />\nWe are secondary school students, we want to make the world a better place! <br />\n<br />\nPlease sign:<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdz5V_o8_YiWRVqSsNi9tP1abAHkU0cd7TYr69r1wO1_GyFSA/viewform?usp=pp_url\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSdz5V_o8_YiWRVqSsNi9tP1abAHkU0cd7TYr69r1wO1_GyFSA%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dpp_url&d=SfvWO4iieP9%2B5ivoSMB2Bstxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=56ca2aea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdz5V_o8_YiWRVqSsNi9tP1abAHkU0cd7TYr69r1wO1_GyFSA/viewform?usp=pp_url</a><br />\n<br />\n#民主路。有你有我，缺一不可"},{"pid":"04b04a30d190245cadf17dd54c79a599946b0b36","tid":1381972,"uid":69334,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:09:53.000Z","msg":"意念係好，但驚義士太集中埋一齊做野會好易比人尋仇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi